# Python API Template Rules (templates/python-api/)

**Repository**: idp-templates  
**Inherits from**: `/idp-templates/.cursorrules` (root)

## Overview
Backstage template for scaffolding Python FastAPI services with database support, full CRUD operations, and comprehensive testing.

## Template Purpose
- Generate FastAPI REST APIs
- Include SQLAlchemy models
- Database migrations with Alembic
- OpenAPI documentation built-in
- Production-ready configuration

## Template Variables
```yaml
${{ values.name }}              # API name
${{ values.description }}       # Description
${{ values.owner }}             # Owner
${{ values.include_database }}  # Boolean for DB support
${{ values.database_type }}     # postgres/mysql/sqlite
```

## Generated Structure
- FastAPI application with routers
- Pydantic schemas
- SQLAlchemy models
- Database connection pooling
- Health/ready endpoints
- Requirements.txt with pinned versions

## Best Practices
- Include pytest configuration
- Add example tests
- Document API endpoints
- Provide database migration examples
- Include Docker Compose for local development

